HEADWORD: Transported
<hw>Trans*port"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Conveyed from
one place to another; figuratively, carried away with passion or
pleasure; entranced.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Trans*port"ed*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Trans*port"ed*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
